Welcome to the plain and simple BadgeQuest! One of my gems for one of yours, buying type evolutions all the time. I'm attempting to get my badges all to the [b]Titanium[/b] level, and would love your help![hr]
[h3]General Trade Guidelines[/h3][css=text-align:left][ul]
[li]You must give me a date and time of availability for mass trades, i.e. more than two trades at a time. Please do not attempt to send trades until we have confirmed that we are both online to do so.[/li]
[li]Please do not PM me this thread, post instead![/li]
[/ul][h3]Gem Guidelines[/h3][ul][li]I swap in the largest size possible first. I do not break down large or medium gems.[/li][li]Electric Gems, while always needed (even beyond Titanium) are not my preferred swap. If you have anything else to trade I'd strongly recommend offering other types first.[/li][/ul][h3]Evolution Guidelines[/h3][ul][li]My prices are firm, please don't try to haggle with me.[/li][li]Availability of currency is subject to change at any time, but I do trade in credits, gold, and zophan.[/li][li]I may also consider buying your evolutions with summons, lucky seals, lucky eggs, megastones, and shiny/albino Pokemon. Just ask![/li][/ul][/css][/sc][

